gtksourceview: gtksourceview (GTK Source Code Widgets)
gtksourceview:
gtksourceview: A text widget that extends the standard gtk+ .x text widget 
gtksourceview: GtkTextview. It improves GtkTextview by implementing syntax
gtksourceview: highlighting and other features typical of a source editor.
gtksourceview:
gtksourceview: This is the older 1.8 series, and some applications still require
gtksourceview: this API. It can coexist with gtksourceview2.
